{"id": 1358, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于护肤，你都有哪些（作作的）习惯？", "description": "不保养，皮肤很差，过度保养，毛孔堵塞，所以到底要怎么样？（题图来自：Jenna Arts）", "record_count": 3331, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161130175149zqiucvhYNlaGSyIf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-02T03:00:08Z", "options": [{"id": 139264, "content": "喜欢尝试不同品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229943}, {"id": 190720, "content": "洗脸很用力……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998404}, {"id": 140545, "content": "面膜！面膜！面膜！重要的事情说三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 827913}, {"id": 139266, "content": "一定要咬掉嘴上的死皮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712977}, {"id": 139778, "content": "假期宅在家里   不出门不洗脸  不出门不洗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 284986}, {"id": 140290, "content": "猛拍水，几天拍掉一瓶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742312}, {"id": 139267, "content": "作为一个抹油完全靠灵光一现的女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776715}, {"id": 139268, "content": "游泳", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853833}, {"id": 140548, "content": "除了夏天其他季节都在往身上涂厚厚的身体乳 冬天脸上糊4层早上起来才不会觉得干 沙漠皮奏是我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675506}, {"id": 183813, "content": "多睡觉啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982776}, {"id": 139270, "content": "面对毛孔有一种森森的无力感～ 总觉得现有的肤品都没用什么卵用，然后不停的被各种宣传种草拔草...这都是商家的套路吗…说好的光滑白瓷零毛孔呢…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853839}, {"id": 139272, "content": "看到各种即使不出门也要防晒，防晒不是防黑而是防老化等各种资讯，下定决心买了防晒霜，涂了两次再没用过", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767276}, {"id": 139273, "content": "洁肤最重要，囤货习惯要改", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842791}, {"id": 139529, "content": "全用刮胡泡搞定", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855075}, {"id": 174601, "content": "只有一盒自然乐园或韩束的芦荟胶   一年四季都如此", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 139274, "content": "不要吃的太油腻，多吃水果蔬菜，保持好心情，保证睡眠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183041}, {"id": 139275, "content": "开心就做，不开心什么都不做，就这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726119}, {"id": 178187, "content": "刷完牙洗完脸，涂完水乳之后，睡前必须涂护唇膏，护手霜。。。", "image": "img/option/option/20170313104156FeAO3MjmprKC5s6J", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968481}, {"id": 174604, "content": "一年四季都是冷水洗脸   不用洗面奶   什么水啊  乳啊      \n每天素颜朝天(当然我还是个高中生?)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 139277, "content": "不洗脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853355}, {"id": 139279, "content": "微信红", "image": "img/option/option/20161202204804GaleKJvrZd5qB6zg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853872}, {"id": 233743, "content": "“我基本上半个月洗一次脸”不过男生没这么讲究啦！哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/201709041701355UCWAdRyYDumroF0", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124085}, {"id": 139280, "content": "大学之前只用郁美静……现在只用补水喷雾…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759998}, {"id": 145936, "content": "没有固定护肤品牌但有固定护肤流程", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875385}, {"id": 139281, "content": "不用洗", "image": "img/option/option/201612022048332VdfwMrL9DgGbAHm", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853355}, {"id": 139537, "content": "早上的洗面奶和晚上的洗面奶，是不同的。一个是保湿温和的，一个是清洁力强的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855090}, {"id": 202770, "content": "同学间一直在宣扬不用洗面奶洗脸。。。个个皮肤好到炸\n只有我不用洗面奶就黄黄黄黄黄下去吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029436}, {"id": 139282, "content": "明细账", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853872}, {"id": 140562, "content": "一定要用洗脸刷，不然感觉没洗干净…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817074}, {"id": 173842, "content": "做为一个男人表示不懂，保湿的有那些，面膜那些好用的介绍下。祛斑产品又有那些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955524}, {"id": 139283, "content": "用比较便宜的爽肤水做水膜，感觉不错，比较省钱，效果也很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838180}, {"id": 148756, "content": "早晚温水洗脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883784}, {"id": 173844, "content": "有那些男性护肤产品好用，求介绍，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955524}, {"id": 139797, "content": "不用毛巾抹脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834579}, {"id": 139286, "content": "熬夜?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839284}, {"id": 139287, "content": "一定要是号称天然护肤品的 不相信片状面膜 很注意保湿防晒 以及上护肤品的手法和力度 最重要还是运动和饮食清淡啦~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705692}, {"id": 230167, "content": "自以为是的认为先用去黑头的 然后用去油的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028404}, {"id": 173847, "content": "有哪些男性护肤产品好用，求告知", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955524}, {"id": 139800, "content": "去年买的面膜 今年快过完了 还没拆 摊手", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240981}, {"id": 140312, "content": "打开水龙头，关掉水龙头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857118}, {"id": 140314, "content": "没什么特别的方式，就是尽量不长时间看电脑不熬夜，用一些简单的护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856893}, {"id": 139292, "content": "多睡美容觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853355}, {"id": 139293, "content": "没有专门的护肤方法 更多的时间是洗完脸就躺在枕头上 我能做的就是勤洗一下枕套", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775607}, {"id": 139549, "content": "底子好的自不必说。皮肤肌理的清洁很重要。我选用天然原材料冷制手工皂。【罗蔓手工生活馆】", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673436}, {"id": 139805, "content": "为了颜值可以不顾一些。\n护肤这点小事绝对义不容辞。\nBecause I am a gay.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659191}, {"id": 277533, "content": "绝不用毛巾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324881}, {"id": 139294, "content": "不忌口", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853950}, {"id": 143902, "content": "护肤不单是为了皮肤好也是在平抑自己的购买欲。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814443}, {"id": 139296, "content": "保证睡眠真的很重要啊，我要睡了，晚安", "image": "img/option/option/20161202231223mwABUudMKDHSPiyl.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853971}, {"id": 139297, "content": "不熬夜最重要…呃，什么，我在熬夜发帖…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853978}]}